            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1699442191846-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1699442191846-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>white long grain rice</strong>, <strong>outer lemongrass</strong> <strong>layers </strong>and<strong> </strong>175ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[230ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[350ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> to a pot with a lid and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving – this is your <strong>lemongrass rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1699442194832-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1699442194832-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1699442194832-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
