          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1699442199394-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 20 min, add the <strong>spinach </strong>to the pan and cook, uncovered, for a further 2-3 min or until the spinach has wilted and the sauce has thickened slightly – this is your <strong>Filipino-style chicken breast & lentil curry</strong></p><p>Discard the bay leaf[ves]</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1699442203397-x200.jpg",
