            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Filipino-style chicken breast & lentil curry</strong> over the <strong>lemongrass rice </strong>(discard the lemongrass!)</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>quick</strong>-<strong>pickled chilli</strong> (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
